*couchdb-1.6.1 (29 Dec 2014)

  29 Dec 2014; Dirkjan Ochtman <djc@gentoo.org> +couchdb-1.6.1.ebuild:
  Version bump couchdb to 1.6.1 (fix bug 501332, bug 529826, bug 520372)

  02 Nov 2014; Sven Vermeulen <swift@gentoo.org> couchdb-1.5.1.ebuild,
  couchdb-1.6.0.ebuild:
  Remove sec-policy/selinux-* dependency from DEPEND but keep in RDEPEND (bug
  #527698)

  10 Aug 2014; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> couchdb-1.5.1.ebuild,
  couchdb-1.6.0.ebuild:
  QA: drop trailing '.' from DESCRIPTION

  29 Jun 2014; Dirkjan Ochtman <djc@gentoo.org> couchdb-1.6.0.ebuild:
  Allow erlang-17 for couchdb-1.6.0

